BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 630 Td (Step 3: Press the green call button at the bottom to start the call.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 600 Td (Step 4: Hold the phone to your ear or tap the speaker icon for speakerphone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 570 Td (Step 5: When finished, tap the red End Call button to hang up.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 540 Td (Step 6: To call someone in your contacts, tap Contacts and find their name.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 510 Td (Step 7: To redial someone, tap the Recents tab to see your call history.) Tj ET

endstream
