BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 167.76 740 Td (Lesson 11: Online Banking Safety) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 690 Td (Step 1: Only download your bank's official app from the app store.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 660 Td (Step 2: Never access banking through links in emails or text messages.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 630 Td (Step 3: Set up fingerprint or face recognition for secure login.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 600 Td (Step 4: Create a strong password with letters, numbers, and symbols.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 570 Td (Step 5: Enable notifications so you get alerts for every transaction.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 540 Td (Step 6: Always log out when you finish your banking session.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 510 Td (Step 7: Never do banking on public WiFi - use your home network or mobile data.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
