BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 176.4 740 Td (Lesson 19: Staying Safe Online) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 690 Td (Step 1: Never share passwords with anyone, even people claiming to be support.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 660 Td (Step 2: Be suspicious of messages asking you to click links or verify accounts.) Tj ET
