BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 630 Td (Step 3: App crashing? Close it completely and reopen, or delete and reinstall.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 60 600 Td (Step 4: Battery draining fast? Lower screen brightness and close unused apps.) Tj ET
